ðŸ“‹ ATTRIBUTE REFERENCE

WINDOW ATTRIBUTES:
  Name              - Window title
  Width, Height     - Window size
  Theme             - "Dark" or "Light"
  DevMode           - Enable auto-refresh ("true" or "false")
  Version           - App version string
  Author            - Author name
  Icon              - Path to .ico file
  DarkMode          - Enable Windows dark mode ("true")
  Mica              - Enable Mica effect (Windows 11) ("true")
  Blur              - Enable blur effect ("true")
  Acrylic           - Enable acrylic effect ("true")
  OnLoad            - Handler to run on app start

CONTROL ATTRIBUTES:
  Name/x:Name       - Control identifier (for Logic reference)
  Text              - Text content
  Content           - Button/Label content
  Background        - Background color (#RRGGBB or color name)
  Foreground        - Text color
  FontSize          - Font size in pixels
  FontWeight        - "Normal", "Bold", "Light"
  Width, Height     - Size (number or "Auto")
  MinWidth, MaxWidth, MinHeight, MaxHeight
  Margin            - Outer spacing ("all" or "left,top,right,bottom")
  Padding           - Inner spacing
  Opacity           - 0.0 to 1.0
  Visibility        - "Visible", "Collapsed", "Hidden"
  IsEnabled         - "true" or "false"
  IsReadOnly        - For TextBox ("true" or "false")
  HAlign            - "Left", "Center", "Right", "Stretch"
  VAlign            - "Top", "Center", "Bottom", "Stretch"
  CornerRadius      - Border corner radius
  BorderThickness   - Border width
  BorderBrush       - Border color
  Orientation       - For StackPanel ("Horizontal" or "Vertical")
  ToolTip           - Tooltip text
  Cursor            - Cursor type ("Hand", "Arrow", etc.)

GRID PLACEMENT:
  Row               - Grid row (0-based)
  Column            - Grid column (0-based)
  RowSpan           - Span multiple rows
  ColumnSpan        - Span multiple columns

EVENT HANDLERS:
  onClick           - Click event
  onChange          - Text changed event
  onEnter           - Enter key pressed
  onValueChanged    - Slider/Progress value changed
  onMouseEnter      - Mouse enter
  onMouseLeave      - Mouse leave

